These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, weightlifting, sailing
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | sailing | weightlifting | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, lettuce, pomegranate
1. the person eating lettuce is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating raspberry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | raspberry | pomegranate | lettuce |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, chess, reading
1. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | chess | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, punk, hip-hop
1. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | metal | hip-hop | punk |

